VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT pickle\.loads\(|yaml\.load\(\s*[^,\)]*\)|marshal\.loads\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:yaml\.safe_load|Loader=SafeLoader|trusted|allowlist|from_trusted_source
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects unsafe deserialization primitives in framework request/worker flows.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Django Unsafe Deserialization.
